| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4512 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6eee0fb2-83a0-5051-aaef-37b731670d4a"
